---
import PhoneSolutionFeatures from "./phoneSolutionFeatures.astro";
import PhoneSolutionMockup from "./phoneSolutionMockup.astro";
---

<section id="phone" class="py-16 lg:py-24 overflow-hidden w-full">
    <div class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 box-border">

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">

            <div class="space-y-6 text-center lg:text-left">
                <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight text-white">
                    La <span class="bg-linear-to-r from-primary to-secondary bg-clip-text text-transparent inline-block">Solución</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-white/70 leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 text-pretty font-medium">
                    Vera actúa como un filtro inteligente entre tú y las amenazas digitales, simplificando la seguridad para que solo te preocupes de conectar.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="w-full flex justify-center order-3 lg:order-2">
                <PhoneSolutionMockup />
            </div>

            <div class="w-full order-2 lg:order-3">
                <PhoneSolutionFeatures />
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>